data.description: Home on horse property... Escape to your own paradise retreat!  This southwest themed home on nearly 7 acres offers a 4-stall barn, vast pastures, a pristine pool, and a seasonal stream. The barn is being restored before closing. A separate studio with plumbing and electricity can easily be converted to an accessory dwelling unit.  The main house is inviting with a spacious entry, expansive living room with fireplace, open-beamed ceilings in the glass enclosed dining room, and a bright kitchen overlooking the comfortable family room. The downstairs office can be a fourth bedroom. The upstairs  master suite is luxurious with a walk-in closet, attached bath, and spa tub room.  Near Hirschman's Pond and Trailhead, this home provides access to hikes and water activities. Just 2 miles to historic downtown Nevada City, known for Victorian architecture, boutiques, art galleries, and dining. Enjoy local events like the Film Festival and Victorian Christmas.  For outdoor enthusiasts, this wonderful home is surrounded by trails, fishing, boating, and nature experiences. The 16357 Indian Flat Rd community thrives on landscapes, recreation, and community spirit. Start your dream lifestyle here!
